    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is a collector-grade E46 M3, presenting in concours-level condition. This specimen is powered by the S54B32 3.2L atmospheric inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been meticulously addressed, including rod bearing replacement, a comprehensive Double-VANOS overhaul, and structural subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with no bushing deflection, and the engine exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key example for the serious driving purist.",
